#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:11
msgid "Granite 9"
msgstr "Granite 9"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:12
msgid "Build consistent and usable apps more quickly and easily"
msgstr "更快速簡單地創造有一致性且好用的應用程式"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:14
msgid ""
"A companion library for GTK and GLib that provides complex widgets and "
"convenience methods designed for use in apps built for elementary OS."
msgstr ""
"用來與 GTK 與 GLib 一起使用的函式庫，提供設計給 elementary OS 應用程式使用的"
"複雜元件和方便的方法。"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:24
msgid "elementary, Inc."
msgstr "elementary, Inc."

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:32 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:45
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:75 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:107
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:126 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:148
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:162 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:174
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:192 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:229
msgid "Improvements:"
msgstr "改善項目："

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:34
msgid "ListItem uses the context menu cursor when menu_model is set"
msgstr "讓 ListItem 在已設定 menu_model 時使用內文選單游標"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:35 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:49
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:80 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:113
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:134 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:151
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:167 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:177
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:196 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:232
msgid "Updated translations"
msgstr "更新翻譯"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:47
msgid "HeaderLabel now has ellipsize property"
msgstr "新增 ellipsize（加上刪節號）的屬性給 HeaderLabel"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:48
msgid "ListItem now has a menu_model property"
msgstr "為 ListItem 新增 menu_model 屬性"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:59
msgid "New Icons:"
msgstr "新圖示："

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:61
msgid ""
"View icons for columns, grids, lists, and reader mode. Plus horizontal and "
"vertical ellipsis icons"
msgstr ""
"分欄檢視、格狀檢視、列表檢視與閱讀模式的圖示。還有水平與垂直刪節號的圖示"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:62
msgid "Start and End show/hide sidebar icons"
msgstr "左右側邊欄的顯示/隱藏圖示"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:63
msgid "Emoji category icons used by GTK's emoji picker"
msgstr "表情符號分類圖示，GTK 的表情符號選取工具有使用"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:64
msgid "Eye icons required by Gtk.PasswordEntry"
msgstr "Gtk.PasswordEntry 所需要的眼睛圖示"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:66 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:103
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:120 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:184
#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:207
msgid "New Features:"
msgstr "新功能："

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:68
msgid ""
"Box is an orientable widget that includes standardized spacing and linked "
"styles"
msgstr "Box: 一個可指定方向的元件，包含標準留白與已連結樣式"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:69
msgid "ListItem is a standard list widget that includes styles and spacing"
msgstr "ListItem: 標準清單元件，包含樣式與留白"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:70
msgid "ToolBox is a vertical layout widget for top and bottom toolbars"
msgstr "ToolBox: 一個垂直配置元件，供頂部與底部工具列使用"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:71
msgid ""
"new style class constants for labels: CssClass.NUMERIC and CssClass.MONOSPACE"
msgstr "文字標籤用的新的樣式類別定數：CssClass.NUMERIC 與 CssClass.MONOSPACE"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:72
msgid ""
"StyleManager handles automatically setting dark and light modes as well as "
"system accent colors using Portals"
msgstr ""
"StyleManager 利用桌面入口 (Portals) 管理自動設定深色與亮色模式與系統強調色"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:73
msgid ""
"BackButton is a standardized navigation button that activates "
"\"navigation.pop\" and includes a shortcut tooltip"
msgstr ""
"BackButton 是一個標準化的導覽按鈕，會觸發 \"navigation.pop\"，並包含快捷鍵工"
"具提示"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:77
msgid "accel_to_string now uses the word \"Super\" instead of the \"⌘\" symbol"
msgstr "accel_to_string 現在不再使用 \"⌘\" 符號，改用 \"Super\" 一詞"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:78
msgid ""
"HeaderLabel has a new property for H1-H4 sizes and H2 styles are now bolder"
msgstr "HeaderLabel 現在有 H1-H4 大小的新屬性，且 H2 樣式現在更粗"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:79
msgid "CssClass.CARD is now rounded by default"
msgstr "CssClass.CARD 現在預設改為圓角"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:82 data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:136
msgid "Deprecations:"
msgstr "棄用項目："

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:84
msgid ""
"Utils.set_color_primary. Modern apps have moved to more of a split paned "
"design and this style is no longer very fashionable"
msgstr ""
"Utils.set_color_primary。現代應用程式已改用更多分割面板的設計，這個風格已退流"
"行"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:85
msgid ""
"Nearly all of the old `STYLE_CLASS` constants have been deprecated. Some of "
"them have been replaced by `CssClass` constants, others by widgets."
msgstr ""
"幾乎所有舊的 `STYLE_CLASS` 定數都已經被棄用。它們有一些被 `CssClass` 定數取"
"代，其他則是被元件取代。"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:87
msgid "Demo Improvements:"
msgstr "展示 demo 改善項目："

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:89
msgid "More demo pages with more widgets"
msgstr "更多展示頁面，展示更多元件"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:90
msgid "Color scheme switcher in the sidebar"
msgstr "在側邊欄裡包含切換配色方案的按鈕"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:105
msgid "Granite.Bin"
msgstr "Granite.Bin"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:109
msgid "Improve screen reader support for SwitchModelButton"
msgstr "改善 SwitchModelButton 的螢幕閱讀器支援"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:110
msgid "Wrap long labels for SwitchModelButton"
msgstr "讓 SwitchModelButton 將較長的文字標籤折行"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:111
msgid "HeaderLabel: set accessible description"
msgstr "HeaderLabel：設定輔助使用描述"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:112
msgid "ValidatedEntry: set AccessibleState for validity"
msgstr "ValidatedEntry：為驗證結果設定 AccessibleState"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:122
msgid ""
"Toast: add a new dismissed signal that includes the reason for dismissal"
msgstr "Toast：新增包含忽略原因的新的 dismissed 訊號"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:123
msgid "Add STYLE_CLASS_SUCCESS"
msgstr "新增 STYLE_CLASS_SUCCESS"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:124
msgid "HeaderLabel: allow secondary text to use markup"
msgstr "HeaderLabel：讓次要文字也能使用 markup"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:128
msgid "Make building Demo optional"
msgstr "提供是否要編譯範例的選項"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:129
msgid "Demo now uses a modern split-pane design"
msgstr "範例改為使用現代化的分割面板設計"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:130
msgid "DateTime: handle relative datetime when epoch"
msgstr "DateTime：有 epoch 的時候處理相對日期時間"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:131
msgid "MessageDialog: Set last button as focus widget"
msgstr "MessageDialog：將最後一個按鈕設為聚焦元件"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:132
msgid "SwitchModelButton: Remove redundant switch keyboard focusing"
msgstr "SwitchModelButton：移除開關上重複的鍵盤聚焦"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:133
msgid "Load fallback styles for widgets when using Granite.init"
msgstr "使用 Granite.init 時為元件載入備用樣式"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:138
msgid ""
"SettingsPage and SettingsSidebar: these widgets have moved to LibSwitchboard"
msgstr "SettingsPage 和 SettingsSidebar：這些元件已移至 LibSwitchboard"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:150
msgid "Add a withdraw method for Granite.Toast"
msgstr "為 Granite.Toast 加入 withdraw 方法"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:164
msgid "Don't depend on the elementary stylesheet for fallback styles"
msgstr "讓備用樣式表不要依賴主要的 elementary 樣式表"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:165
msgid ""
"Automatically load gresourced stylesheets named \"Application.css\" on "
"\"Granite.init ()\""
msgstr ""
"以 \"Granite.init ()\" 初始化時自動載入名為 \"Application.css\" 的 "
"gresourced 樣式表"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:166
msgid "Add SettingsUri constants for launching System Settings"
msgstr "新增用來啟動《系統設定值》的 SettingsUri 常數"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:176
msgid "Make \"Granite.init ()\" publicly available"
msgstr "將 \"Granite.init ()\" 設為 public"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:186
msgid "Granite.STYLE_CLASS_RICH_LIST for standard Gtk.ListBox row padding"
msgstr "用 Granite.STYLE_CLASS_RICH_LIST 來取得標準的 Gtk.ListBox 列間間隔"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:187
msgid ""
"Granite.STYLE_CLASS_FRAME for adding a border to Gtk.LisBox, Gtk.InfoBar, "
"and others"
msgstr "用 Granite.STYLE_CLASS_FRAME 來為 Gtk.LisBox、Gtk.InfoBar 等等加上邊框"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:188
msgid "Granite.STYLE_CLASS_SIDEBAR for styling application sidebars"
msgstr "用 Granite.STYLE_CLASS_SIDEBAR 來為應用程式側邊欄套用樣式"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:189
msgid ""
"Granite.STYLE_CLASS_BACKGROUND to use the default background color for a "
"widget"
msgstr "用 Granite.STYLE_CLASS_BACKGROUND 來使用元件的預設背景色"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:190
msgid "Add optional secondary text to Granite.HeaderLabel"
msgstr "為 Granite.HeaderLabel 加入非必要的次要文字"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:194
msgid "Allow text in Granite.Toast to wrap"
msgstr "允許 Granite.Toast 的文字自動換行"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:195
msgid ""
"SimpleSettingsPage: Wrap titles and allow description text to go under "
"switches"
msgstr "SimpleSettingsPage：讓標題自動換行，並允許描述文字顯示在開關下方"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:209
msgid "Ported to GTK4! 🎉️"
msgstr "移植到 GTK4 了！🎉️"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:210
msgid "Granite.Placeholder: replaces AlertView and Welcome"
msgstr "Granite.Placeholder：取代 AlertView 和 Welcome"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:211
msgid "SimpleSettingsPage: Allow markup in description"
msgstr "SimpleSettingsPage：允許在描述中使用格式"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:213
msgid "Removals:"
msgstr "移除項目："

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:215
msgid "Application: use Gtk.Application instead"
msgstr "Granite.Application：請改用 Gtk.Application"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:216
msgid "Drawing: Use Gtk.CSS"
msgstr "Drawing：請改用 Gtk.CSS"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:217
msgid "DynamicNotebook: use Adw.TabBar instead"
msgstr "DynamicNotebook：請改用 Adw.TabBar"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:218
msgid "Logger: use GLib.log instead"
msgstr "Logger：請改用 GLib.log"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:219
msgid ""
"ModeButton: Use Gtk.ToggleButton with the \"group\" property and \"linked\" "
"style class instead"
msgstr ""
"ModeButton：請改用 Gtk.ToggleButton 並設定 \"group\" 屬性與 \"linked\" 樣式 "
"class"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:220
msgid "Paths: use GLib.Environment instead"
msgstr "Paths：請改用 GLib.Environment"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:221
msgid "Seekbar"
msgstr "Seekbar（跳轉列）"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:222
msgid "Services.Settings: use GLib.Settings instead"
msgstr "Services.Settings：請改用 GLib.Settings"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:223
msgid "SimpleCommand: use GLib.AppInfo.create_from_commandline instead"
msgstr "SimpleCommand：請改用 GLib.AppInfo.create_from_commandline"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:224
msgid "SourceList: use Gtk.ListBox with the \"sidebar\" style class instead"
msgstr "SourceList：請改用 Gtk.ListBox 並利用 \"sidebar\" 樣式 class"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:225
msgid "StorageBar"
msgstr "StorageBar"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:226
msgid "TextStyle: use style class constants instead"
msgstr "TextStyle：請改用樣式常數"

#: data/granite.metainfo.xml.in:227
msgid "Several functions in System were replaced by GLib.AppInfo"
msgstr "用 GLib.AppInfo 來取代 System 中的一些函數"

#~ msgid "Granite.CssClass.NUMERIC"
#~ msgstr "Granite.CssClass.NUMERIC"
